{
  "stem": "11801.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- of course, my mother could not-- I could not move out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my mother had no means of keeping me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had this tiny room [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with, you know, I think, a little burner and sink or something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't-- didn't have a bathroom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think she used the toilet of the family that rented her the-- this room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in fact, a year ago, I went back to see that house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it had been totally renovated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I-- you know, it was-- I had never been back there before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but, you know, to her, these things didn't pose any problems.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And anything was better than where she came from.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- and my mother was a very upbeat sort of person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was far more introspective and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] moody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't think I had the words.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We, we didn't have the vocabulary at first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't-- you know, as I said, I didn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I no longer spoke German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I hated German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To this day, I can't stand hearing German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I will not speak it if I can get away with it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She, of course, this was her language.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was the only language she spoke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she didn't have, you know, this feeling towards the language, which is stupid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But [LAUGHS] I always shudder when I hear German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so I really didn't want to learn German again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But of course, I had to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because I knew I had to talk with my mother and eventually with my father, since once I came to America, I, I didn't know English.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
